==English==

===Adjective===
'''gluggy'''
# Adjective form of [[glug]].  Used to describe a substance (normally liquid, specifically viscuous) which moves slowly or with some resistance.  Can also be used to describe someone who is lazy or sluggish (displaying the same characteristics.)
#:''The jelly was not yet set, but quite '''gluggy'''.''
#:''The rice was '''gluggy''' (ie it stuck together, or was pasty.)''
#:''The morning after the party I felt '''gluggy'''.''